videos.headline: Frith hauls in a nice pass under pressure for Liberty TD
videos.description: Noah Frith makes a nice grab in the end zone to put Liberty on the board early vs. Maine.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Frith hauls in a nice pass under pressure for Liberty TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Liberty's Louis returns kickoff 97 yards to the house
videos.description: Shedro Louis returns a Maine kickoff 97 yards, avoiding a tackle on his way to the end zone for Liberty's second score of the night.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Liberty's Louis returns kickoff 97 yards to the house) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Liberty's Gandy-Golden palms impressive one-handed catch
videos.description: Stephen Calvert puts it in the air for Antonio Gandy-Golden who makes an amazing catch to help Liberty to a first down and 33-yard gain.
